      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "更进一步，我们不只想说是或否，还想说这个点有多大概率属于红类。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "logistic-regression",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
